{"tid":160083,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯上上簽","createTime":"2017-03-17T12:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T13:35:02.000Z","uid":88921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1745d22373b2bc5da094537e61404fd575d58870","tid":160083,"uid":88921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"作為一個魚拉突 咁既對手真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n講真咁同直接宣佈曼冠軍有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班魚拉突 totally no mood to 捱夜睇波 嗱,我又分析下 首先安咩烈治,唔好玩啦 比利時野，雙殺穩陣<br />\n<br />\n史浩克04,,如果係巴狗就有可觀性(順便可以報上次ga仇)(不過算啦,入到決賽又會見到面) 我真係冇睇過依隊野..曼半力夠WIN,又雙殺<br />\n<br />\n最後決賽,我連名都唔想睇，我地出青年軍練下is ok,又贏<br />\n<br />\n加上我地4大尖刀 朗尼,伊巴,馬達,米希達恩加上關鍵王白蘭特.. 根本場場大炒,,,,<br />\n<br />\n冠軍就一定..係睇下破唔破到得失球.咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,下年歐聯見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手魚拉突..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"76de552491829386c44065bb16f011b91a1c158d","tid":160083,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:35:25.000Z","msg":"明月光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36fd4e66079d0bf5b9ef855841cc80f640866d94","tid":160083,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"打佮咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3f2e3dbab8f1f7c23f4070e978057da5d09b2c","tid":160083,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbe1595b69b5f52c07f579c5096c3f69539e5f91","tid":160083,"uid":88921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關鍵王白連特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輸波關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},